{"id": "29592", "revid": "1211", "url": "https://lij.wikipedia.org/wiki?curid=29592", "title": "Col\u00f2nne", "text": "Cul\u00f3nne l'\u00e9 'na frasi\u00f3n id Cantaluvu ch'a gh'\u00f2 28 abitanti. A s'tr\u00f6va inte l'\u00d2ta Val Burb\u00e0ia a 371m d'altit\u00fcdine, int'ei cum\u00fcne 'd Cantaluvu (Cantalovvu). L'\u00e8 'n pa\u00ecze 'd lingua e tradi\u00e7i\u00f3n-i l\u00ecguri inta Prov\u00e9incia 'd Lisandria."}
